question: Show all chalets and cabins which cost 200 per night.
sql_query1:
SELECT Chalets.Name 
FROM Chalets
WHERE (Chalets.Accommodation = "Chalet" OR Chalets.Accommodation = "Cabin") AND Chalets.Price_Per_Night = 200.0
sql_query2:
SELECT Chalets.Name 
FROM Chalets
WHERE Chalets.Accommodation = "Chalet" OR Chalets.Accommodation = "Cabin" AND Chalets.Price_Per_Night = 200.0
interpretation1: Show both chalets and cabins where either cost 200 per night.
interpretation2: Show all the chalets, also show the cabins which cost 200 per night.
